SELECT 
    'CreatePurchaseDocumentLine' || '::' || "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID"     AS "ID",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID"                                             AS "PurchaseDocumentLine",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID"                                             AS "PurchaseOrderLine",
    "PurchaseDocument"."ID"                                                 AS "PurchaseDocument",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."DocumentCategory"                               AS "DocumentCategory",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."CreationTime"                                   AS "Time",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."CreatedBy_ID"                                   AS "ExecutedBy",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."CreationExecutionType"                          AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "o_custom_PurchaseDocumentLine" AS "PurchaseDocumentLine"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_PurchaseDocument" AS "PurchaseDocument"
        ON "PurchaseDocumentLine"."Header_ID" = "PurchaseDocument"."ID"
WHERE "PurchaseDocumentLine"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL
